itle as second viscount, was christened Anthony Maria Browne. In Camden's Remains (p. 44), referred to in Delicie Literarise, occurs Thomas Maria Wingfield; and there was also a Sir Edward Maria Wingfield. The name appears to have been adopted in the latter family from Mary, daughter of Henry VIII. Compare Notes and Queries 5th S. ii. 73, 316, 478. Marie is frequently found as a male name in France and in other parts of the Continent."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Maria Schwaban was born about 1270, in Suffolk, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Warin FitzHugh. She died about 1343, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 75."},"et":{"about 1270–about 1343":"umbes 1270–umbes 1343","1270–1343":"1270–1343","1300–1377":"1300–1377","about 1270":"umbes 1270","1377":"1377","1300":"1300","1343":"1343","about 1343":"umbes 1343","about 1300":"umbes 1300","1270":"1270","Kentwell, Suffolk, England":"Kentwell, Suffolk, England","Suffolk, England, United Kingdom":"Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, England","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1270–about 1343":"noin 1270–noin 1343","1270–1343":"1270–1343","1300–1377":"1300–1377","about 1270":"noin 1270","1377":"1377","1300":"1300","1343":"1343","about 1343":"noin 1343","about 1300":"noin 1300","1270":"1270","Kentwell, Suffolk, England":"Kentwell, Suffolk, England","Suffolk, England, United Kingdom":"Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, England","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1270–about 1343":"environ 1270–environ 1343","1270–1343":"1270–1343","1300–1377":"1300–1377","about 1270":"environ 1270","1377":"1377","1300":"1300","1343":"1343","about 1343":"environ 1343","about 1300":"environ 1300","1270":"1270","Kentwell, Suffolk, England":"Kentwell, Suffolk, Angleterre","Suffolk, England, United Kingdom":"Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, 